Enhanced logging with structured INFO-level logs across all services and controllers

- Disabled SQL query logging in application.yml (show-sql: false)
- Added @Slf4j and comprehensive logging to CustomerServiceImpl, ProductServiceImpl, OrderServiceImpl, SubscribeServiceImpl
- Added INFO-level logging to all controllers with efficient combined log statements
- Updated entities with proper annotations and relationships
- Added refresh token functionality (RefreshTokenRequest, RefreshTokenResponse)
- Enhanced JWT service and customer authentication
- Updated Dockerfile and build configuration
